Using advanced photometric technology, I have developed a new corpse01/hobo texture that takes a picture of its viewer and turns it into a lazy retexture.

This mod retextures both the player and ragdoll variants of this model. Made from a soyjak I found on the floor, wojak whatever idk dude. This model is the Hobo from DarkRP

Also check out my other mod "Removed Real Corpse from Hobo Texture" :)
